-stonewashed skinny jean features an exotic cheetah print and zippered hems.
-Belted waist.
-Zip fly with a signature shank closure.
-Five-pocket styling with rivets at the front points of wear.
-Zippered detail at each hem.
-Machine washable. Imported.
- SIZE 28 
- never been worn ! 
Printed jeans are super trendy right now! Pair this with a sheer black blouse and killer red sandals for a party outfit! For a more casual approach, throw an oversized burgundy top and some ankle boots with it. 
* retails for 108.00

name: Sachin + Babi open sleeve dress
description:
-black boatneck dress with open sleeves
-white sequin detail on the sleeves
-White center back zipper
- size 10 ( relaxed fit )
Every girl needs a LBD and this one is super unique due to the open sleeves with the white sequin. Dress is down with flats, make it professional with a belt and a blazer over top and wear it out with some killer animal print heels! This dress can go anywhere!

name: Sparkle and Fade sequin crop top
description:
-Cute cropped top with sequin detailing from Sparkle & Fade
-Luxe blended mohair construction
-Boxy silhouette
-Narrow tank straps. 
-size large ( fits M/L)

name: Sachin + Babi printed dress
description:
- orange, blue and white printed dress
- 3/4 sleeves that can be undone to full length
- detached back detail ( you can see it in the pictures from side angles) 
- comes with a slim black belt ( we styled it with a different belt )
- black outline around buttons and collar 
-size 10 ( meant to have an airy fit, the person wearing it in the picture is a size 6 so I would say anyone from a 6-12 can fit into this nicely)
- retailed for 600$ 
Printed dress are very trendy right now and this one is especially great because of the back detail. The great thing about this dress is that you can wear it to just about anywhere, your shoe will indicate where you are going but the dress can be worn to casual events as well as formal ones!

name: American Apparel knit tank
description:
-Cream colored knit tank 
- Size large 
Really great piece for layer throughout the year or to simply pair with some denim and flats for a casual outing!

name: Maison Martin Margiela faceless watch bracelet
description:
- faceless watch bracelet that can also be worn as a necklace ( you can see that in the picture ) 
- never been worn 
Really great modern jewelry thats very versatile ad can be worn with all your outfits!

name: Maison Martin Margiela for H&M trompe l'oeil leggings
description:
- trope l'oeil fishnet legging 
- elastic waist 
- size ( US 10 , EUR 40 )
- very form fitting
- never worn

Really cool leggings to pair with all your over sized tees and tanks!

name: American Apparel striped nylon lace shorts
description:
-Top: Nylon Tricot (80% Nylon / 20% Elastane) construction
- Bottom: Nylon Spandex Stretch Lace (90% Nylon / 10% Elastane) 
-Elastic waistband
- size large ( very form-fitting )
 
This is an awesome pair of shorts for the summer! Throw an oversized black or white tee shirt over it and some sneakers and you're good to go! I also like to pair these shorts underneath high waisted shorts and let the lacy part show !

name: American Apparel red lace crop top
description:
-A sheer and sexy stretch floral lace crop top with short sleeves and a scoop neck.
-Nylon Spandex Stretch Lace (95% Nylon / 5% Elastane) construction
- size large ( very form-fitting)

Pair this with high waisted black distressed shorts and some white sneakers for a chill day look. For an evening look, pair it with a chiffon black maxi skirt, cropped blazer and gold sandals!

name: Lilac open knit sweater
description:
- long sleeve lilac colored sweater
-open knit ( it is sheer so I would recommend a black tank underneath)
- size small
Super cute sweater you can pair with blacks greys and whites! The lilac color is very appropriate for summer and you can pair this sweater with skirts or shorts and because it isn't super thick it can even be tucked in!

name: Kensiegirl olive knit with see-through back
description:
- olive color green sweater
- see through in the back 
- very light sweater ( perfect for colder summer nights)
- scooped neckline
- size medium 
Super cute and unique light weight sweater for the summer! 
Tuck this into any of your high waisted shorts with a pair of oxfords for a day look! Because of the see through back, this can definitely be used for a sexy outfit! Pair it with skin tights black jeans or leather pants with a pair of pointy toed pumps, gold accessories and a killer red lippie!

name: Creme colored knit sweater
description:
long sleeve knit sweater in cream color
two small pockets in the front
scooped neckline
size S/M
Pair this with a light denim shorts and ballet flats for a relaxed day look and for the night, put this over a short black ( or really any color) chiffon skirt with a camel color shoe!

name: Rachel Comey sheer plaid dress
description:
- short sleeve checkered dress
- made of  100% silk 
-an asymmetrical scoop neck and placket
-draped hem 
- size 10 ( meant to be a relaxed fit )
- comes with a matching slip 
-featured on the spring 2012 runway show
This is a really fun and unique dress perfect for formal events. Literally all you need are some strappy black or nude sandals, a small gold clutch and a red lippie!

name: Free People button up dress
description:
- Long sleeve button down dress 
- longer in the back
- size large ( meant to have an oversized fit )
- because the dress is slightly sheer, it comes with matching slip
This dress is super versatile because it can be worn throughout the year.  For summer, leave it loose, roll up the sleeves, pair it with chunky platforms in taupe or beige and some gold accessories. For the colder seasons, belt it over some black tights and throw a denim jacket over it.

name: Topshop green velvet skirt
description:
- maxi green velvet skirt
- size 8 
-stretchy waist band 
This skirt will touch the ground unless you are 5 10' and up like me! I like to style it two ways, either leave it as long as possible or hike it up to " midi " length. 
Pair this with a black top and oversized light denim jacket for a great easy look! 
- I am also selling the oversized David Bowie tee ( from topshop as well) It is completely sheer in the back.

name: Zara oversized blouse
description:
- tunic blouse with colorful feather patterns
- wrist length sleeves which are oversized 
- oversized fit throughout
- slightly longer in the back
- size xl ( the top is meant to be oversized but it is not sloppy or baggy on the body. If you were a size 6 and up this will look great on you)

name: Stuart Weitzman black pumps
description:
- pointy toed black pump
- about 3 inch heel 
- size 11 
This is a must for every female wardrobe! They are not too high so they  make for good party shoes! Obviously this can be paired with anything, no closet is complete without a black pump.

name: Rachel Roy one sleeve blouse
description:
- oversized chiffon animal print blouse
- one side is a batwing arm sleeve and the other side sleeveless
- size XL - although it is a bigger size, this top is meant to be loose fitting. 
This top looks especially great with red, black, light denim or olive green bottoms. If you want to do a skirt then I would do either a pencil high waisted skirt of a long fitted maxi skirt in either of those colors!

name: Vintage camel clutch
description:
- rectangular shape camel clutch with gold accents
- it comes with a removal strap so you can go from clutch to shoulder bag 
- large zipper pocket on the inside
This is such a great evening bag that you can switch from clutch to shoulder bag if you find yourself needing both hands! This is a great replacement to your typical black clutch and can be paired with all colors including black!

name: Vintage black and gold shouler bag
description:
- black shoulder bag with gold detailing surrounding it
- adjustable strap
- interior and exterior pockets
- clean interior ( as you can see in the last picture) 
Very pretty bag that can easily be worn with anything, day or night!

name: Gold woven leather shoulder bag
description:
- woven leather all around
- adjustable straps
- drawstring closure 
- one pocket on the inside 
- clean interior ( you can see in last pic )
Gold work with everything and this bag can work in the evening and during the day !

name: Vintage leather patchwork backpack
description:
- leather patchwork in blue red and brown
- multiple pockets ( on the outside, inside and the back )
- clean interior ( as you can see in the last picture )
This is a great bag for a person that likes to spend the summer by a lake or just walking around and you want to carry more things but still keep it fashionable!

name: Rachel Roy shredded tank
description:
- cheetah printed long tank
- shredded in the back
- size large
If you do not want to go braless or do not own one of the band-less bras then a black lacy bra will look just as good ( as pictured ) This is a really fun top to go out, just put on a pair of light denim and a cropped leather jacket ( so you can see how its shredded in the back) and some killer red heels!

name: Vintage heeled oxfords
description:
-black lace up oxfords with 2 inch heel 
- size 8 1/2
These are totally staples in a wardrobe. They can work with denim or shorts for a casual look but you can also pair this with a pencil skirt and dressy blouse !

name: Trotters leather loafers
description:
- brown basket weave leather all around 
- Premium leather upper and padded insole
- flexible, lightweight non-slip outersole.
- size 12N which means 12 narrow, My mom is an 11 and theyre a little big on her so I would say theyre more like an 10 1/2 -11 narrow. 
- Super comfy and stylish shoe to throw on over some light denim boyfriend jeans with a striped top and some ray bans. This would also look great styled with an airy floral dress belted with a matching brown belt.

name: Vintage Bally loafers
description:
- Black loafers from historical label Bally
-Gold Bally logo sign in the front
- about an inch heel 
- basket weave leather detail 
- size 8 1/2

name: BCBG Max Azria cheetah bandange skirt
description:
- camel/black/cheetah print
-Flattering and fitted heavy knit that smooths the figure
-reaches mid-thigh
-Size medium ( these are very stretchy so if you are anywhere between a 6-12 this skirt would fit you just as good !)

name: Vintage Italian loafers
description:
- one inch black loafers
- gold buckle detailing in the front
- size 35 1/2 italian ( 5 1/2 us ) 
These are great everyday shoes, work an androgynous look and wear yours with a pant suit. For a more feminine look, pair this with a short floral chiffon skirt with a white tee tucked into it and a cross body bag !

name: 100% leather pointy toe creme pumps
description:
- creme pumps with cross detail in the front and studs 
- about  3 inch heel 
- size 9 1/2 
- 100% leather, made in Italy 

Pointy pumps are back in full force with labels like Dior coming out with new styles season after season! Like Dior, this pump also has the cross detail in the front to give it an edge!

name: BCBG Paris floral chiffon vest
description:
- long chiffon floral vest
- Long in the front, short in back style 
- no lining so sheer throughout 
- size medium (relaxed fit)
This vest looks great on burgundy pants, black tank and some flats. You could also belt this over a long black maxi dress, floppy hat and ankle boots for a dressier look!

name: Club Monaco bohemian dress
description:
-subtle western influence airy chiffon dress, printed with kaleidoscopic diamonds. 
- half-placket buttons to the smocked elastic waist, which gathers the skirt. 
-Banded single-button cuffs circle the forearm and add volume to the 3/4 sleeves.
- Slip dress lining
-size 12  
- 100% silk 
- You can either belt this look or wear it drop waist style 
Super great piece for summer, its super comfy and airy. I would pair this with a brown belt and tan booties or wedges for a daytime casual look. This dress would work great in the fall with navy or brown tights with tan colored shoes.

name: Sequined tee
description:
- sequined black t-shirt with blue and pink pattern
- 100% silk with rayon lining 
- size medium
This is the perfect evening top, dressy enough that a pair of black skinny jeans and some pumps or strappy sandals will do! For another look, throw this over a a fitted maxi dress with a matching blue or pink sandal!

name: Free People cropped sweater
description:
- long sleeve cropped sweater
- it's completely sheer throughout ( open knit )
- sleeves are oversized 
- size Medium 
- This sweater looks fab on a pair of high waisted denim shorts or over a high waisted black skirt or pant with some burgundy shoes.

name: Helmut Lang blazer
description:
-  cap sleeved blazer in taupe
- cropped in the back, long in the front
- one pocket on each side
- one button closure
- large 
This jacket would look great left open over a bright color fitted tank with some dark wash denim and ballet flats.

name: Vintage checkered blazer
description:
-green and teal checkered blazer
- two button closure as well as two pockets 
-100% wool
-size 8
- This is a great statement blazer to have. I would pair this over a black fitted dress with some ankle boots or for a more relax look, over a black crop top and light denim shorts with some converse!

name: Polka dotted chiffon buttown down
description:
- long sleeve button down
- the buttons end mid way 
- one size fits all
- looks fab on fitted burgundy pants/skirt and a taupe color shoe! I would also style this on white high waisted shorts/skirt !

name: Rachel Roy Signature blouse
description:
- long sleeve printed blouse
- Victorian style neckline 
- ruffles all around the buttons 
- slightly oversize sleeves
- sheer throughout but because of prints its not obvious
- I would pair this with some black skinnies and booties for a casual look or tucked into a pencil skirt with some pumps for a dressy look. 
- Size ten

name: Joe Fresh yellow python button dow
description:
- Long sleeve button down
- yellow python print
- Size small
- For a casual look, pair this with some skinny denim ( blues, blacks or greys) and some ankle boots. If you want something for the evening, then tuck it into an aline black skirt with strappy sandals.

name: Printed vintage shawl
description:
- slouchy oversized sweater
-dramatic dolman sleeve detail
- teal colored with slashes of pink and fuchsia as prints
- made of rayon
-one size fits all ( oversized fit)
Throw this over some fitted black high waisted pants or shorts with some converse for a relaxed look. For a more professional approach,  tuck in a white button down into a black pencil skirt with this dramatic piece to jazz it all up.

name: Vintage red blazer with leather collar
description:
- Oversized blazer with leather collar 
- Size L -XL ( meant to have an oversized look to it )
- made of wool
- interesting fact: designed by Jeremy Scott when he worked for Braemar. 
- This is sucha  great piece if you are wearing a black outfit and want to jazz it up!

name: Aritzia tri-color button blouse
description:
- long sleeve button down
-mainly olive color with creme and orange outlines
-100% silk
- slightly sheer
- size large ( it is a small large, so more like medium I would say) 
Because there are three different colors on it, you can choose to match it to either one of the secondary colors. Ex: tuck it into a creme colored skirt with orange sandals or throw it over an orange pant with some creme shoes. This would also look great over light/dark denim!

name: Floral chiffon blouse
description:
- long sleeve chiffon blouse 
- the sleeves are made to be slightly oversized
- more fitted on top and wide on the bottom
-size large
- unlined
- style this with fitted dark red or mustard yellow jeans and some ballet flats for a casual look

name: Vintage highwaisted polka dot shorts
description:
- polka dotted vintage shorts
- bermuda shorts lenght
- these shorts can easly be unisex
- Size M/L
- Polka dot looks best paired with anything red!

name: Cheap Monday sheer jumper
description:
- Bright yellow short sleeve jumper
- open knit throughout so a little sheer 
-size M/L
- I would style this over a short chiffon skirt ( black, greys, blues) and ankle boots. For an even more casual look, pair this with light colored denim and some flats or oxfords.

name: Burnt velvet button down
description:
- long sleeve velvet button down with burn velvet patterns
- size large ( meant to have a relaxed fit )
- This top looks great left open on top of a black maxi dress with some funky silver accessories! Pair this with a black cami and some denim for a casual look  !

name: Unif floral kimono
description:
- 3/4 sleeve floral kimono from Unif
- colorful floral print throughout 
- longer in the back, shorter in the front 
- M ( oversized fit )

name: Studded collar chiffon button down
description:
- Short sleeve black button down
- silver studs on each collar  
- slightly longer in the back and on the sides
- size M/L - meant to have a relaxed fit
- I would pair this with dark fitted bottoms ( skirt, shorts or pants) and a jean jacket to lighten it up

name: Vintage printed jacket
description:
- long sleeve light weight jacket
- floral prints all over it 
- gold button closures
- sizes M/L
- This is a great summer jacket to throw over your shorts and skirts. I especially love to pair this jacket with mustard yellow pieces!

name: Oversized leopard print button down
description:
- vintage chiffon blouse
- One size fits all 
- animal print all over
Great top the spice up a business suite or pair this with leather leggings and killer stilettos for a night out!

name: Floral button down with denim collar
description:
- 100% cotton
- long sleeve button down
-denim collar
-size medium 
Looks fab tucked in or left open over fitted dress!

name: cut out shoulders button up
description:
- long sleeve button up with cut out shoulders
-size M/L
-great to tuck into high waisted skirt/jeans or keep it untuck over a pair of skinnies

name: tri colored cropped jumper
description:
- long sleeve cropped jumper
- blue. white and red coloring
- size L ( could fit a medium because it is meant to be slightly over sized)
- looks really cute on a chiffon skirt or high waisted pants

name: high low velvet tank
description:
- burgundy color
- short int he front, longer in the back
-tank style ( no sleeves)
-size M
-looks fab with high waisted pants/shorts
